The Telegraph - Calcutta
 Aravinda wife seeks divorce 
Colombo: Ace Sri Lankan batsman Aravinda de Silva faces civil action with his wife seeking divorce, court officials said on Wednesday. De Silvas wife, Sarita Rajendran, filed action in the Colombo district court on Tuesday seeking divorce and Sri Lankan Rs 50 million for damages, the officials said. Rajendran also sought custody of their two-year-old son, Sampras. (PTI)  Copyright 
